The company serves the automobile industry, industrial and special gearbox manufacturers, machine tool manufacturers, and others. It also exports its products. The company was formerly known as Anglo American Marine Co. Ltd. Jainex Aamcol Limited was incorporated in 1947 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}